messages.title: How to Check Your Balance
messages.body:

messages.title: Just Walk Out Market Tips!
messages.body:
Quick Tips for Automated Markets

Powered by Amazon Just Walk Out + Triton2Go

Getting In
• Wait for the gate to close before scanning your QR code.
• Anyone entering right after you will be charged to your account—make sure the gate shuts behind you!

While You Shop
• Bag items as you go (BYO bag or buy one in-store).
• You will be charged for anything you take off the shelf, even if you hand it to a friend
• Put items back on the shelf = no charge.
• Dropped something? Ask staff for help—don’t grab a replacement yourself.
• Can’t reach something? Ask a staff member for assistance.

Checking Out
• Your receipt will show up in the Triton2Go app (Inbox > Receipts).
• Think there’s a mistake? Go to Homepage>Dining Support Form in the app and send a screenshot of your receipt for faster help.

messages.title: UC San Diego Men's Basketball Tickets & Schedule
messages.body:
UC San Diego Men's Basketball Student Tickets

Redeem Your FREE UC San Diego Men's Basketball Tickets!

Students must claim their free tickets on the Monday prior to each home game.

Redeem your tickets here: https://bit.ly/ucsdstudenttix

Student Claim Dates:

Claim your tickets on the Monday listed below to attend that week’s game(s):

  • Claim on Monday, October 20 → For the game on Friday, October 24 vs. Cal State San Marcos

  • Claim on Monday, January 26 → For the game on Thursday, January 29 vs. UC Santa Barbara
